Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.20,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:00.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,能夠如此輕易地躲開這利樁的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這個世界上恐怕也就只有你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.42,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,紅方的Lancer啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:12.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,原來如此 你正是適合阻擋在此地之王面前的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不敢當 異國的王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:17.70,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,然後我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:22.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,對你來說 這利刺既是攻擊 又是防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,既是示威 也是恐怖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:26.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,穩定領地 穩定居城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:31.67,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,穩定應當守護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:36.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,也就是說 你想要僅憑自己形成一個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這是靠對祖國的愛完成的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:44.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,還是出自身為王的責任感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,是想揭露余的內心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:50.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是異國的王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.20,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這裡並沒有你的麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.60,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,王也許是孤高的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:05:01.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是也不存在沒有麾下單獨上戰場的王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.52,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,然後 我是英靈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:08.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,即便與一國為敵也無所畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:11.97,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:15.27,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,獨自與這國家為敵也無所畏懼嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:18.67,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不愧是英雄！ 不愧是余的敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:22.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 你早已在余的死亡陷阱之內！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:35.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,很遺憾 余的寶具的本質並非「利樁」…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,刺出的利樁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.97,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這一概念本身就是寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:43.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:48.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,只要你還在余的領域之內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,就無法逃離這個寶具！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,來吧 結束這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.00,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,紅方的Lancer！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:12.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,火焰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,有趣…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,哈哈哈哈哈哈哈這就是叛逆！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:51.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,叛逆就是我的一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:04.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,很好 再多來一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,再對來一些！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:13.60,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:17.70,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,他叛逆的精神化作實體的姿態！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,吾輩的大綱並沒出錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:27.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,還真有如此恐怖的寶具啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:27.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:30.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那正是「疵獸的咆吼」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:30.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,{\fs31\pos(696,600)}Crying Warmonger
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,能夠將受到的傷害變換為魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:35.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,並化作自己的力量的寶具！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,斯巴達克斯既是劍鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:43.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,也是為被虐待的人們挺身而出的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:46.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,他的生存方式在成為從者後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:49.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,便被升華成為了那寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.77,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 雖說能將傷痛化作力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,也並非無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:56.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,正是如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,極限已經近在眼前了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:04.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那位大英雄馬上就會放出一生最強的一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.70,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,然後消失了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.70,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,接著那正是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.97,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我們御主的革命劇的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.57,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我的鐵拳即是愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,來吧！ 接受我的愛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:27.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,休想逃走！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:29.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:49.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,在那裡嗎 壓政者！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.27,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什麼…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:56.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那個方向是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:07.60,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,真是煩人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:10.52,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你這樣的戰鬥方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,已經是對騎士王的侮辱了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:19.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,齊格！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,已經到極限了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:29.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,齊格！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你的身體…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,雖然不懂怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不過已經要結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,反正說到底不過是贗品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:39.60,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,是不可能敵得過我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,紅方的Berserker？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:49.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,壓政者啊 在我的愛中毀滅吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:56.77,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你這 骯髒的肉球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,少開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:09.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,Saber 快點撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:11.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,立刻離開那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:14.17,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那傢伙非常不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:22.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,好… 好噁心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:29.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不要動 傷口很深
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:30.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那邊的兩位 請快逃跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這裡很危險 快一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:36.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你是… 為什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.77,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,明明這條命是妳救回來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:45.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 我覺得 無論如何都得這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:47.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.27,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不要責怪他！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:54.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,他是為了保護身臨險境的我而戰鬥的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,然後才會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:00.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,必須快點離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:06.00,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不 我已經動不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你才應該快點離開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:12.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你不是應該在這裡毀滅的從者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:14.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那麼 起碼黑方的Ri…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:14.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:15.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不要不要不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你也不是小孩子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我說不要就是不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:24.57,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我也不能逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,如果Ruler是我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.67,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,也不會把他丟在這裡逃走吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,唉 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.47,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你都這麼說了也就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:41.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我也有不能逃離這裡的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:48.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,請不要離開這裡 絕對！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:50.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,斯巴達克斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:00.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我不能讓你這樣的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:03.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,傷害無辜的民眾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,時機已到…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:15.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我的一擊將破壞所有的壓制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:18.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,粉碎所有的權力！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:21.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這就是斯巴達克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:27.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我的旗幟啊 請守護我的同胞吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,吾的神明在此！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,{\fs31}Luminosite Eternlle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:17.71,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,啊 還活著 得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:20.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,好痛… 請讓開一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:21.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:26.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,各位都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:27.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:40.97,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,死在這裡吧 Lancer！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,大地啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,太慢了！ 天空啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:12.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,牆壁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:23.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,寶具嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:25.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,梵天啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:25.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,{\fs31}Brahma
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,御主正在召集我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,下次再決一勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什麼？ 你！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:43.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:46.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,達尼克嗎… 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:52.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:14:58.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:01.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:10.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,難道…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:46.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,真沒想到居然還有這樣的手段…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:54.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,現在 長久以來一直守護的尤格多米雷尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,被逼入了絕境… 這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:01.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 這種程度的苦境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:08.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,在這百年來 已經有過無數次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:13.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,八十年前 尤格多米雷尼亞得到衰落的預言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:16.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,無法再次作為魔術師出人頭地的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我參加了冬木的聖杯戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,利用了國家與軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:25.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,有時甚至連協助者都被我當成棄子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,為了延長壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.00,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不斷吞噬他人的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:31.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,現在就連我自己都不知道自己是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,即便如此 我也要得到大聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:40.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,怎麼可能又會將其交給別人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:43.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,難以置信…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:45.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:47.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,大聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:49.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:52.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,如果是從者就能明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那就是我們所彼此爭奪的大聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,看來我必須得去一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:06.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這將是質問紅方的最後機會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:11.57,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,之後我會好好說教齊格你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:15.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我明白了 我會做好心理準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:33.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,看來這邊還沒有探知術式的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:35.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:44.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,看來 來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:46.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:59.20,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,省得余去找你了 紅方的Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,剛才失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:07.42,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,就在這裡重新戰鬥 來對你盡到禮數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:10.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你要由我來打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這次餘一定會將你刺成串的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,怎麼了？ 黑方的Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:04.52,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,跟剛才不一樣 動作裡缺乏精彩之處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:06.57,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,孤高的王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:10.17,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,在救援到來之前要休息嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:13.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,即便與多人作戰我也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:22.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什麼…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:39.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,余的力量在這難道行不通嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:44.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,還是魔力的供給被抑制了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是紅方的Lancer啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:52.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,余即便賭上龍公之名也要擊敗你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:19:59.67,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那裡是紅方的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:06.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,無法完全發揮身為王的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:08.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,是贏不了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:12.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,達尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:13.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你知道關於余的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:20.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不遜又令人極為不快的傳說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,後世之人總是對死者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:29.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,擅自抱有幻想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,沒錯 總是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:37.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 余絕對無法原諒！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,玷汙余之一族的名聲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:44.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,將餘光榮的生存方式籠罩上陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:48.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,即便是後世 也永遠應當被定罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,正是如此 王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:54.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,延續家名是我們的榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:21:00.00,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,決不能允許被卑劣之人擅自傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:03.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,賭上瓦拉幾亞大公的名譽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:06.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,必須防止進一步的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:09.42,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,因此余要託付給聖杯的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:13.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那就是將那口口相傳的骯髒的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:16.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,從余的歷史中抹消…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:18.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,遵命…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:21.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,所以必須要贏得這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是達尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:26.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,雖然你也應該明白 但還是要多加提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:30.47,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,絕對不要讓余使用「那個」寶具…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:33.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,哪怕要難看地敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:36.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,余也絕對不會使用「那個」寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:41.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,若是你使用令咒強迫余的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:45.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,之後的事 就不必我多說了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:49.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,明白了「吾王」…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:54.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 既然如此就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:58.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,應當守護的是尤格多米雷尼亞的存續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:01.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,應當到達的是「根源的漩渦」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:05.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,無論如何都需要大聖杯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:07.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,抱歉了Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:10.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我要打出王牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:14.85,Default-CN,,0,0,0,,第11話 永遠的光輝
